Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.80,0:00:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.84,0:00:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使受了伤也无妨  不转移目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.84,0:00:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想热切、激烈地生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.84,0:00:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我永不放弃的坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.84,0:00:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想紧紧抱着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.84,0:00:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.84,0:00:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去或痛楚都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.84,0:01:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引导至鲜明的、一瞬间的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.84,0:01:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.84,0:01:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胸中的鼓励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.84,0:01:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向你延续而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.91,0:01:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,创造完全和平是有条件的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其一就是把所有武器毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.29,0:01:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其二就是从人们身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除去战斗的意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.27,0:01:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令天秤座坠落，只有这行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是通向完全和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去地球的人会憎恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.08,0:01:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星会倚赖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上只要有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.28,0:01:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相同的错误就会不断重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.23,0:02:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯认定这里是其葬身之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那并非因为他在藉着战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.61,0:02:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻求干脆的了断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.61,0:02:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他打算独自背上肃清人类的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.95,0:02:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛应该发觉那一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该发觉了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.63,0:02:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终话\N[最后的胜利者]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵的撤退情况如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,80%平安生还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，机动战士就损毁严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.34,0:03:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,67%被毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，在回收的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把剩下的机动战士毁灭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.55,0:03:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有武器都不可留在地球圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.22,0:03:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是特列斯大人的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也一直以完全和平为目标呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎你，女王陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜女王?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.34,0:03:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你别再那样称呼我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了，迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后拜托你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去对付外面那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，别在这附近战斗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那会妨碍我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们跟敌人说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.75,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是个失去灵魂的空壳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你完成替令尊报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.27,0:04:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,报仇和战斗也到此为止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，轮到问题的中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天秤座和万年和平号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经预测了遇害范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于坠落地点也已发出避难警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避难警告? 别胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那两艘舰造成的破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非只是质量的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一那两艘舰的动力炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.56,0:05:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿过大气层在地面爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.83,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使一时的破坏是数百公里也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为爆炸而升上天空的大量灰尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会遮挡太阳光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为整个地球带来寒冷的天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.35,0:05:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球会变成不能住人的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要避过此劫就要把它们移离轨道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又或者在大气层外炸毁它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两个方法都很困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，还有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一部钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在万年和平号的动力部份附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是希洛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，大概是钢弹02
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，那些家伙也一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.64,0:05:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确还有希望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.14,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他钢弹呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，四处都是MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直不停战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每一次都不停地令心灵受创
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我的心早已变得空空如也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.03,0:06:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许没有身为人类活下去的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我非活下去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有要回去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.31,0:06:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本已经没有要回去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.95,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能站起来吗?卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.19,0:06:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有个请求…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管我，她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心，卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她并非脆弱得会迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务完成，现在会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，如果今次工作顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就畅饮极品香槟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.34,0:07:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好主意呢，但要没酒精的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵特尉，诺茵特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是MO-II，请答话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵特尉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.92,0:07:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呼唤她有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你早晚会明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题是时间的流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会否比我的预测快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，联络上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久违了，特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在旁观希洛和杰克斯的战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那些映象接到这里的频道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经不是OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会服从命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.11,0:08:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是命令啊，我在求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为渴望和平的同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传送给地球圈的所有人看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.83,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹在自相残杀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争不是结束了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对卫星和地球来说都没有意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.18,0:08:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他们有必要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.85,0:08:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这场战斗都是为了保护卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(后宇宙殖民历)AC195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗的历史将要落幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果这两人不战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平就不会来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们感觉到了吗? 这场战斗的悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.46,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们能看到吗? 这场战斗的悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是各位为了和平以强硬姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,达成的问题决议所致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安代表?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来她还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.01,0:09:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通的喷射不能改变轨道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.15,0:09:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好拆除动力炉内的压力限制器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令其他东西暴走以制止暴走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我们惯用的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你们不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坎斯吗? 很久不见…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你们不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死我们也不要紧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.28,0:09:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们真麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们要妨碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.65,0:09:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的流星行动多少次才满意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.45,0:09:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由钢弹替希洛‧唯报仇就够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次和今次也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你们没更改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给钢弹驾驶员的命令内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.43,0:10:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类的觉醒应该会更快来临啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.30,0:10:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，但我们对地球和人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有更高一点的评价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们今次也要妨碍你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和特列斯一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搬出大义来保护弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.61,0:10:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那绝对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会帮到弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造出弱者的是强者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名为地球的强者的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造出名为卫星的弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后把其赶进绝境之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分出胜负了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾经讨厌弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不知自己何时会被攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经常提心吊胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能相信别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不出想说的任何一句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种家伙令我受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是强者令他们那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，任何地方也没有强者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类全是弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你也是弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万年和平号和天秤座\N正离开地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天秤座的一部份正坠落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到卫星代表团发出的声明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们卫星代表团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于世界国家的战败宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.29,0:12:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在发表所有卫星的一致决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们撤回对白色獠牙的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渴望和地球的世界国家和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，即使在任何理由之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也不会采用战斗行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们强烈希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.77,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界国家同意这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再者，因为我们态度不鲜明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.84,0:12:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而令这场战争里\N许多人受到伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们深表歉意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶! 还不行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要尽量破坏它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,减少对地球的破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结束了，杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，还没完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还没承认自己是弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.68,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有动力系统吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然有，即使只是那区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界也难逃冬天的来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹02，03，04，05
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达A区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王兄和希洛不是在那里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两人打算\N战个不死不休吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊! 你们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星凭着自己的判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,踏上了完全和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行为是无意义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始终是沾满血腥的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今，我不会逃避这罪孽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决胜负啊! 希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未来应该充满希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何不杀我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜会伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这区域仍在向地球坠落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去破坏这舰的动力系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种碎片坠落地球前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把它粉碎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.74,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未到最后不放弃希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我驾驶这机体后学回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功的可能性近乎零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.22,0:15:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…那比坐以待毙好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧? 卡特尔少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大…大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不可以来这种地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真见外啊，我们也要帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今，人多好办事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你批准! 卡特尔少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对不起，大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的方法是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆装置吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天秤座A区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,200秒后冲入大气层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.37,0:16:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平需要的东西还有一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是关怀和了解别人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坚强的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你那样的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.62,0:16:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太单纯，而且太仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.05,0:16:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是否就没有生存的资格吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我去到哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也会活下去给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.07,0:16:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为比谁都认真的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后会有期! 希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动力系统爆炸确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但一部份仍在坠落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并未烧毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰身坠落的破坏无可避免
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫钢弹们撤退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,零式啊，引领我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接住! 你遗下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷，到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.41,0:17:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家先撤退，我还能战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经尽了力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样死去只是白死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把能源炮交给希洛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷，你听到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到，我们会妨碍希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，马上离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲入大气层了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有机体在它前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…飞翼零式?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样也好，不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.39,0:18:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，他做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他在大气层的高热中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我认识的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直把任何困难都克服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，他能够信赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.37,0:18:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为希洛会赐予所有人希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
